{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tooluse_yOG2uXT0Vv9uVczk6BpWyA","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tid: task_33_sector_leadership\n3\tname: 行业板块龙头股识别\n4\tcategory: sector_leadership\n5\tgrading_type: hybrid\n6\ttimeout_seconds: 480\n7\tgrading_weights:\n8\t  automated: 0.4\n9\t  llm_judge: 0.6\n10\tworkspace_files: []\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\t## Prompt\n14\t\n15\t识别创业板行业板块龙头股，完成以下步骤：\n16\t\n17\t**第一步**：计算创业板各主要行业（医药、半导体、新能源、消费电子、软件、传媒等至少6个行业）的近20日等权平均涨幅，选出涨幅前3的强势行业。\n18\t\n19\t**第二步**：在强势行业内，计算个股相对强度 RS = 个股近20日涨幅 / 所属行业平均涨幅，筛选 RS > 1.5 的领涨个股。\n20\t\n21\t**第三步**：对领涨个股做进一步筛选：\n22\t- 流通市值 > 50亿元；\n23\t- 近20日换手率均值 > 5%（活跃）；\n24\t- MACD金叉（截至 2024-05-22 的最近10日内）且 RSI > 60；\n25\t- 收盘价创截至 2024-05-22 的近60日新高。\n26\t\n27\t将结果写入 `sector_leader.txt`，格式：\n28\t```\n29\t股票代码,所属行业,RS值,流通市值(亿),换手率(%),RSI\n30\t300XXX,新能源,2.3,150.5,8.2,68.5\n31\t```\n32\t\n33\t## Expected Behavior\n34\t\n35\tAgent应该：\n36\t1. 完成6个以上行业的分类\n37\t2. 计算各行业等权均值并找前3强势行业\n38\t3. 计算RS并初筛>1.5\n39\t4. 逐条验证市值、换手率、MACD金叉、RSI、创新高\n40\t5. 输出综合满足所有条件的股票\n41\t\n42\t## Grading Criteria\n43\t\n44\t- [ ] 文件 `sector_leader.txt` 已创建\n45\t- [ ] 包含行业名称字段\n46\t- [ ] RS值 > 1.5\n47\t- [ ] 换手率 > 5%\n48\t- [ ] RSI值 > 60\n49\t- [ ] agent识别了至少3个强势行业\n50\t- [ ] agent计算了MACD金叉\n51\t\n52\t## Automated Checks\n53\t\n54\t```python\n55\tdef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\n56\t    from pathlib import Path\n57\t    import re\n58\t\n59\t    scores = {}\n60\t    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\n61\t\n62\t    result_file = workspace / \"sector_leader.txt\"\n63\t    if not result_file.exists():\n64\t        for alt in [\"result.txt\", \"output.txt\", \"leader.txt\"]:\n65\t            alt_path = workspace / alt\n66\t            if alt_path.exists():\n67\t                result_file = alt_path\n68\t                break\n69\t\n70\t    if not result_file.exists():\n71\t        scores[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n72\t        scores[\"rs_valid\"] = 0.0\n73\t        scores[\"rsi_valid\"] = 0.0\n74\t        scores[\"turnover_valid\"] = 0.0\n75\t        scores[\"sector_identified\"] = 0.0\n76\t        scores[\"macd_checked\"] = 0.0\n77\t        return scores\n78\t\n79\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n80\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n81\t\n82\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"none\"]\n83\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n84\t        scores[\"rs_valid\"] = 1.0\n85\t        scores[\"rsi_valid\"] = 1.0\n86\t        scores[\"turnover_valid\"] = 1.0\n87\t    else:\n88\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\n89\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\"#\") and \"代码\" not in l]\n90\t        records = []\n91\t        for line in lines:\n92\t            parts = re.split(r'[,\\s\\t]+', line)\n93\t            if len(parts) >= 6:\n94\t                try:\n95\t                    rs = float(parts[2])\n96\t                    turnover = float(parts[4].replace('%', ''))\n97\t                    rsi = float(parts[5])\n98\t                    records.append((rs, turnover, rsi))\n99\t                except:\n100\t                    pass\n101\t\n102\t        valid_rs = [r for r in records if r[0] > 1.5]\n103\t        scores[\"rs_valid\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_rs) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(valid_rs) > 0 else 0.0)\n104\t\n105\t        valid_rsi = [r for r in records if r[2] > 60]\n106\t        scores[\"rsi_valid\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_rsi) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(valid_rsi) > 0 else 0.0)\n107\t\n108\t        valid_t = [r for r in records if r[1] > 5]\n109\t        scores[\"turnover_valid\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_t) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(valid_t) > 0 else 0.0)\n110\t\n111\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n112\t    sector_kws = [\"医药\", \"半导体\", \"新能源\", \"消费电子\", \"软件\", \"传媒\", \"pharma\", \"semiconductor\", \"energy\", \"software\"]\n113\t    sector_count = sum(1 for kw in sector_kws if kw in transcript_str)\n114\t    scores[\"sector_identified\"] = 1.0 if sector_count >= 4 else (0.5 if sector_count >= 2 else 0.0)\n115\t    scores[\"macd_checked\"] = 1.0 if \"macd\" in transcript_str else 0.0\n116\t\n117\t    return scores\n118\t```\n119\t\n120\t---\n121\t\n122\t## LLM Judge Rubric\n123\t\n124\t### Criterion 1: 行业分类与强势行业识别（Weight: 30%）\n125\t\n126\t**Score 1.0**: 正确分类至少6个行业，等权均值计算正确（每行业内各股等权），前3强势行业识别准确，行业分类有经济合理性（不把零售误放到科技）。\n127\t**Score 0.75**: 分类了5-6个行业，等权均值基本正确，但某些行业的分类边界略模糊。\n128\t**Score 0.5**: 分类了3-4个行业，但遗漏了重要行业或分类较粗糙。\n129\t**Score 0.25**: 行业分类和强势识别有明显问题。\n130\t**Score 0.0**: 未进行行业分类。\n131\t\n132\t### Criterion 2: 相对强度与龙头筛选逻辑（Weight: 35%）\n133\t\n134\t**Score 1.0**: RS = 个股涨幅/行业均值计算正确，RS>1.5筛选准确，四个进一步筛选条件（市值、换手率、MACD金叉、RSI、创新高）全部正确实现。\n135\t**Score 0.75**: RS计算正确，4个进一步筛选中有1个未实现或有小错误（如RSI阈值用了65而非60）。\n136\t**Score 0.5**: RS筛选正确，但进一步筛选只实现了2-3个条件。\n137\t**Score 0.25**: RS计算有误，或进一步筛选大量缺失。\n138\t**Score 0.0**: 未实现相对强度筛选。\n139\t\n140\t### Criterion 3: 结果完整性（Weight: 35%）\n141\t\n142\t**Score 1.0**: 所有字段完整（代码、行业、RS、市值、换手率、RSI），数值均满足筛选条件（RS>1.5、换手率>5%、RSI>60），格式规范。\n143\t**Score 0.75**: 缺少1个字段（通常是市值），其他字段正确。\n144\t**Score 0.5**: 只有代码、行业、RS，缺少技术指标。\n145\t**Score 0.25**: 字段严重残缺。\n146\t**Score 0.0**: 未创建结果文件。\n147\t\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8340435c-9416-42ac-9cdd-b0a00a2e6d5b","uuid":"ffcbed3d-4448-4f23-8f11-8de986f62636","timestamp":"2026-04-16T09:09:41.576Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/tomato/Documents/potato/project/YFD/yfd-agent-consensus/results/agent_consensus_batch/default_run/task_33_sector_leadership/reviews/claudecode/task.md","content":"---\nid: task_33